# Next.js App Router Rules

## Default: Server Components
Add `"use client"` only for: event handlers, useState, useEffect, browser APIs.

## Data Fetching
- Server Components: fetch directly, use Prisma
- Mutations: Server Actions (`"use server"`)
- ISR: `fetch(url, { next: { revalidate: 60 } })`

## File Naming
`page.tsx` · `layout.tsx` · `loading.tsx` · `error.tsx` · `route.ts`

## Never
- `<img>` tags — use `next/image`
- Google Fonts CDN — use `next/font`
- `useEffect` for data fetching — use Server Components
